profile:
Lake of Bays Eavestrough and Siding is a trustworthy and dependable company servicing the Muskoka Region and surrounding areas. Whether you need exterior solutions for your home or business, our positive reputation in Northern Ontario comes from our exceptional customer service, attention for detail, and top quality materials. Call 705-706-5406 for a free estimate.

Professional and quality siding, roofing and eavestrough contractor in the Muskoka Region and all surrounding areas. We are fully licensed, insured and offer year round service for all your exterior solutions.


Services offered:
Eaves trough repair & installation
Siding contractor
Repair/replace all types of siding
Roofing
Gutter guard installation
Roof top Snow Removal
Ice Dam Removal
Maintenance and Repair of House Exterior


Free Quotations available!
